# Projects

Things I've built and actually run. Mostly self-hosted, mostly Go/Elixir, all scratching a real itch.

## Running services

=> https://werdz.ca Werdz — multiplayer definition-bluffing word game
=> https://mermaidarium.com Mermaidarium — render Mermaid diagrams to images, metadata baked in
=> https://eventshare.app Eventshare — privacy-respecting calendar event sharing
=> https://quotes.onewheelgeek.net Quote Hole — collect and vote on your crew's best quotes

## Tools & infrastructure

=> https://github.com/jclement/pullpilot PullPilot — compose-aware Docker auto-updater with soak windows and health-gated rollback. It keeps this very server fresh.
=> https://github.com/jclement/gatecrash Gatecrash — self-hosted tunnel server; my answer to "do I really need Cloudflare for this?"
=> https://github.com/jclement/drillbit DrillBit — stop SSH-ing into machines just to poke at your databases
=> https://github.com/jclement/megaclaude Megaclaude — sandboxed Claude Code in Docker
=> https://github.com/jclement/owg-fyi capsule — the Gemini + web server rendering this page right now

